        "Description": "Today in Whittleton Creek is a really strange mission. It all starts when a client named Janus asks us to come and murder a jogger named Amelia Garros, who is disturbing his own runs and peace. When Janus&apos; son Gunther Mueller hears about this he can&apos;t stand it, and decides to ask us to murder his father, and pay with his father&apos;s inheritance. However, Janus gets a tip from somewhere that the son has hired men to murder him, and asks us to murder Gunther at the same time. Good luck 47. Have fun!",
